item.title: CVE-2023-7164|2024-06-06T13:04:21.160Z -- unknown -- backwpup
item.description: The BackWPup WordPress plugin before 4.0.4 does not prevent visitors from leaking key information about ongoing backups, allowing unauthenticated attackers to download backups of a site's database.
